citation:Description.dsDescription:Text:
Replication data for analyses described in "Pathophysiological responses of pine defensive metabolites largely lack differences between pine species but vary with eliciting ophiostomatoid fungal species" by Cale et al. (2019; Tree Physiology). 

Please see the Read Me file for specific details on dataset contents.

Related Publication.Citation: Cale JA, Klutsch JG, Dykstra CB, Peters B, Erbilgin N. (2019). Pathophysiological responses of pine defensive metabolites largely lack differences between pine species but vary with eliciting ophiostomatoid fungal species. Tree Physiology. DOI: 10.1093/treephys/tpz012.
